snippet.title: Lonely Mountains: Downhill - Misty Peak Free DLC Trailer
snippet.description: It's time to ⛰️🚵‍♂️↘️ again! Our new free DLC "Misty Peak" is out now on all platforms! It's an entirely new trail and comes along with new challenges and a sweet customization set. See you on the mountain!
